  "text": "This deepening silence about women's sports in mainstream televised news and highlights shows is of particular concern for sports studies scholars, especially when considered alongside the fact that the world of sports is no longer a ''male preserve,'' in which boys and men enjoy privileged and exclusive access to sport participation opportunities [CITATION_1] . To be sure, there is an expanding array of media sources of sports information, including Internet websites, which fans of women's sports can tap for news about their favorite athletes or teams.",
